  "text": "Analysis of carer Social and Personal Activities ( [CITATION_1] .88, P < 0.001). Significant predictors included PwP cognitive impairment (\u03b2 = .34, P < 0.001), duration of caregiving (\u03b2 = \u2212.18, P < 0.01), PwP mobility (\u03b2 = .17, P < 0.01), and carer age (\u03b2 = .13, P < 0.05).",
